flowchart TD
    A[Probe opens codex-command-exec-control-stream] --> B[Daemon streams READY output]
    B --> C[Probe sends wrong processId write]
    C --> D[Daemon returns write mismatch error]
    D --> E[Probe sends correct write on same connection]
    E --> F[Daemon forwards live write and streams echoed PING]
    F --> G[Probe sends wrong processId terminate]
    G --> H[Daemon returns terminate mismatch error]
    H --> I[Probe sends correct terminate on same connection]
    I --> J[Daemon ends process and returns final result]
